These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, october, january, june, april
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, family, satire, western, zombie
5 different games are played: go, bridge, poker, domino, snooker
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: zinnia, poppy, lily, aconite, azalea
 1. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the person who growszinnia is the person watching crime movies##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
10. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who growslily##1
11. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person playing bridge and the person watching zombie movies##2
12. the person playing domino is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
13. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Birthday      | february        | october | april     | january   | june |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | family      | western | zombie   | crime    |
| Game   | domino  | bridge     | go | poker | snooker  |
| Flower           | poppy | lily      | azalea     | aconite   | zinnia     |

