.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, october, february, september, march
City: hamburg, venice, boston, london, hannover
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, indian, polish, spanish
There 5 different types of food: eggplant, nectarine, artichoke, strawberry, banana
 1. the person eating banana is in the middle##1
 2. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person eating banana##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the person eating nectarine is between the chinese and the person traveling to hannover##2
 6. the person eating strawberry is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 8. the indian is the person traveling to london##1
 9. the indian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
11. the indian is the person who's birthday is in february##1
12. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Birthday         | september | july | march    | october  | february    |
| City   | hannover    | venice       | boston      | hamburg | london        |
| Nationality   | spanish   | dutch     | chinese    | polish  | indian     |
| Food     | artichoke    | nectarine | banana | strawberry | eggplant |

