.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, argentine, nigerian, japanese, british
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, baccarat, bolivar, tiparillo, havana
5 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, go, backgammon, canasta
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, rowing, tennis, volleyball
 1. the british is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
 3. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1
 4. the siglo-smoker is in the middle##1
 5. the british is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the argentine is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 7. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 8. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 9. the person playing go is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is the tiparillo-smoker##1
11. the nigerian is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
12. the japanese is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
13. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the havana-smoker and the nigerian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Nationality         | chinese | british     | nigerian   | argentine   | japanese |
| Cigar   | havana  | baccarat | siglo | tiparillo | bolivar        |
| Game   | go      | mah-jongg      | backgammon       | canasta       | bridge       |
| Sport         | basketball | volleyball  | tennis    | badminton    | rowing        |

