.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
5 different games are played: billiard, whist, backgammon, go, bridge
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, dunhill, bolivar, havana, ritmeester
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, funk, indie, reggae, rock
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, ice-hockey, golf, climbing, parkour
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 2. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 3. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is between the fan of reggae and the person playing go##2
 5. the person playing whist is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 7. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 8. the ritmeester-smoker is the fan of funk##1
 9. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
10. the fan of reggae is the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the havana-smoker is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
12. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the fan of indie##1
13. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Game          | bridge  | backgammon     | go   | whist     | billiard |
| Cigar         | ritmeester | aristoff    | bolivar  | havana | dunhill   |
| Music-Genre   | funk        | dubstep    | rock     | indie     | reggae    |
| Sport   | ice-hockey    | golf | climbing | parkour | basketball   |

