.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, november, october, december, may
There are 5 different favourite colors: lilac, ivory, blue, black, light-blue
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, lawyer, manager, social-worker, writer
House: palace, townhouse, colonial, victorian, gothic-revival
 1. the townhouse house is on the right of the dancer##1
 2. the person who likes black is on the left of the palace house##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the victorian house##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is between the townhouse house and the person who likes lilac##2
 5. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the colonial house##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who likes black##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the lawyer##1
 8. the writer is on the left of the colonial house##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the dancer##1
11. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
12. the social-worker is on the left of the dancer##1
13. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Birthday   | december       | may       | august   | october      | november    |
| Color       | light-blue | black        | lilac       | blue       | ivory |
| Job        | writer     | lawyer        | social-worker | dancer        | manager  |
| House      | victorian | colonial | palace      | gothic-revival | townhouse  |

