The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, taxi, train, van, bike
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: november, april, july, march, june
 1. the engineer is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the mechanic##1
 3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the person drinking water is between the bartender and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is the person driving the bike##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is on the far right##1
 9. the mechanic is on the right of the person driving the train##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
11. the dancer is between the bartender and the person who's birthday is in april##2
12. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person driving the van##1
13. the bartender is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | water      | sprite   | fanta   | soy-milk   |
