10. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the french##1
11. the person playing canasta is between the ranch-style house and the owner of the dog##2
12. the townhouse house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
13. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |    5    |
