.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: iris, dahlia, tulip, balloon-flower, lily
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, drawing, reading, traveling, video-games
There are 5 different nationalities: british, colombian, dutch, brazilian, australian
House: modern, ranch-style, palace, wooden, victorian
 1. the australian is between the ranch-style house and the colombian##2
 2. the dutch is on the left of the brazilian##1
 3. the person who growsdahlia is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the person who growsiris is on the right of the australian##1
 5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 7. the modern house is on the right of the victorian house##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the dutch is on the far left##1
11. the palace house is between the dutch and the person who's hobby is reading##2
12. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
13. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Flower    | tulip       | balloon-flower    | lily | dahlia  | iris        |
| Hobby       | video-games | card-games | reading  | traveling | drawing    |
| Nationality       | dutch        | brazilian   | colombian  | australian   | british |
| House   | wooden       | palace      | victorian      | modern | ranch-style  |

