.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, milk, sprite
There are 5 different favourite colors: green, yellow, ebony, orange, lilac
The people have 5 different hobbies: rock-climbing, video-games, writing, singing, magic-tricks
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, water-polo, rowing, basketball, skateboarding
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 2. the person who likes orange is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who likes ebony##2
 3. the person drinking milk is the person who likes orange##1
 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the person who likes lilac and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
10. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
11. the person who likes ebony is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
12. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola         | milk      | iced-tea | sprite     |
| Color           | yellow | ebony | orange | lilac    | green  |
| Hobby   | singing  | video-games    | rock-climbing | writing    | magic-tricks |
| Sport   | rowing  | water-polo        | cricket   | basketball    | skateboarding     |

