.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: parkour, badminton, lacrosse, golf, handball
5 different games are played: badminton, go, whist, snooker, bridge
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, january, july, september, december
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, car, helicopter, jet-ski, ship
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing go##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person playing badminton and the person who's birthday is in june##2
 6. the person playing badminton is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person driving the airplane and the person who's sport is handball##2
 8. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is parkour##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Sport         | handball  | lacrosse | golf   | badminton      | parkour |
| Game   | badminton   | snooker    | go | bridge | whist      |
| Birthday           | july | january    | june       | september     | december      |
| Transport     | helicopter | ship        | airplane  | car        | jet-ski    |

