.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, hot-chocolate, tea, cola
5 different pets are kept: dog, cat, mouse, rabbit, ferret
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, electronic, reggae, rock
5 different games are played: snooker, chess, go, billiard, poker
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is between the person playing billiard and the fan of rock##2
 3. the fan of rock is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is the fan of ambient##1
 5. the fan of ambient is between the person playing poker and the fan of electronic##2
 6. the person playing poker is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is the fan of reggae##1
 8. the person drinking tea is the fan of blues##1
 9. the person playing snooker is the fan of blues##1
10. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person playing go##1
11. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
12. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate    | cola  | coffee  | almond-milk      | tea |
| Pet   | cat    | ferret   | rabbit | mouse | dog   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | ambient    | rock    | reggae       | blues         |
| Game   | billiard  | chess | poker    | go     | snooker      |

 